# Planned LangGraph architecture for Gate 1 review (edgeless Command routing).
flowchart TD
    START([START]) --> collect_signals[collect_signals]
    collect_signals --> predict[predict]
    predict --> decide[decide]
    decide -->|action required| execute[execute]
    decide -->|no_op or policy block| finalize[finalize]
    execute --> finalize
    finalize --> END([END])
